flowchart LR
    U[User] --> D[TPC-DI Driver notebook]
    D -->|picks workflow type, SF, generator| Setup[setup.py]
    Setup --> CreateJobs[Driver creates two jobs]
    CreateJobs --> DG[Datagen Workflow]
    CreateJobs --> BM[Benchmark Workflow]

    DG --> DGNB[tools/data_gen.py]
    DGNB -->|spark_or_native_datagen| Choice{which generator?}
    Choice -->|spark default| Spark[spark_runner.py<br/>distributed PySpark<br/>serverless]
    Choice -->|native| Digen[digen_runner.py<br/>DIGen.jar subprocess<br/>DBR 15.4 + Photon]
    Spark --> SOut[/Volumes/.../spark_datagen/sf=N/]
    Digen --> NOut[/Volumes/.../sf=N/]

    BM --> Bronze[Bronze: read raw files]
    SOut -.read.-> Bronze
    NOut -.read.-> Bronze
    Bronze --> Silver[Silver: SCD2 dims + staging facts]
    Silver --> Gold[Gold: fact tables]
    Gold --> Audit{Incremental mode?}
    Audit -->|yes| AuditRes[automated_audit_results table]
    Audit -->|no| Done[Benchmark complete]
    AuditRes --> Done
